body:
This PR takes cares about api error responses. Normalizes the responses following the structure:
```json
{
   "detail": { 
       "code": "rubrix.api.error::SomeErrorType",
       "params": {
           "msg": "Some error description"
       }
   } 
}
```

The `code` attribute is always a string value, the `params` section could change depending on the error type (the code), giving more contextual details about error.

Only Generic error (http status 5xx) won't include detailed info since could be compromise the infrastructure security
